{"tid":2242650,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家唔好再幫沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)推post","createTime":"2020-10-14T07:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T20:55:22.000Z","uid":48234,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8e64cbe65abec95e69bcb90305132437849b2a6a","tid":2242650,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:06:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n最近沙皮狗經常違反板規證據:<br />\n沙皮狗請回應 有冇報章轉載權； 請LIHKG嚴肅跟進#133680侵犯版權問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194433</a><br />\n<br />\n擁有分身證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/GpbQh7RN/YOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FGpbQh7RN%2FYOU.jpg&h=eacd9956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"9c73acd2ee557af6d4b18176e50f44d13b6f8e04","tid":2242650,"uid":374184,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T08:41:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1dea0ed1a94781e2e3e7a111219651f70179a170","tid":2242650,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212b12d3ec8a41a88cab67d31596c89096842500","tid":2242650,"uid":62025,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"支持老鳳狙擊垃圾"},{"pid":"4f4719ff1283ce57187112ed565a20175af9135b","tid":2242650,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"212b12d3ec8a41a88cab67d31596c89096842500","tid":2242650,"uid":62025,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"支持老鳳狙擊垃圾"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"俾佢追吠到覺得煩，係時候要反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98125585ea6f16bf76e59a52125e60291d636c43","tid":2242650,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52d182b06e6c7e9caeb06dabc2c424530683c030","tid":2242650,"uid":62025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f4719ff1283ce57187112ed565a20175af9135b","tid":2242650,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quo